    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings erected in coastal areas to house men, lifeboats and equipment to aid shipwreck victims; usually maintained by volunteers or government agencies.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
